    <title>curl: Multiple Vulnerabilities</title>
    <synopsis>Multiple vulnerabilities have been found in curl, the worst of which could result in arbitrary code execution.</synopsis>
    <product type="ebuild">curl</product>
    <announced>2022-12-19</announced>
    <revised count="1">2022-12-19</revised>
